<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Glassmorphism Login</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{

display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
height:100vh;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea,#764ba2);

}

.card{

width:350px;
padding:40px;
background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);
backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
border-radius:20px;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);
box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.3);

}

h1{

color:white;
text-align:center;
margin-bottom:25px;

}

input{

width:100%;
padding:14px;
margin:10px 0;
border:none;
outline:none;
border-radius:10px;
background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);
color:white;

}

input::placeholder{

color:#eee;

}

button{

width:100%;
padding:14px;
margin-top:15px;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
background:white;
color:#6c63ff;
font-weight:bold;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;

}

button:hover{

transform:scale(1.03);

}

.links{

display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
margin-top:20px;

}

.links a{

color:white;
text-decoration:none;
font-size:14px;

}

.footer{

text-align:center;
margin-top:25px;
color:white;
font-size:13px;

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<h1>Welcome Back</h1>

<input
type="email"
placeholder="Email">

<input
type="password"
placeholder="Password">

<button>

Login

</button>

<div class="links">

<a href="#">Forgot Password?</a>

<a href="#">Sign Up</a>

</div>

<div class="footer">

Made with HTML & CSS ❤️

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
